{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"Slot-Index","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Slot Index"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Valid slot indices have to be in range of 0 ..< "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/Whiteboard\/documentation\/Whiteboard\/Whiteboard\/slotCount"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"While a slot index has to be an integer value within that range, it is advisable to use a type-safe alternative in Swift, such as a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"RawRepresentable"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"enum"},{"type":"text","text":" whose "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"RawValue"},{"type":"text","text":" represents the corresponding slot index.  This can be achieved by creating an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"enum"},{"type":"text","text":" that conforms to the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"WhiteboardSlot"},{"type":"text","text":" protocol, e.g.:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["enum MyWhiteboardSlot: Int, WhiteboardSlot {","    case firstWhiteboardSlot","    case secondWhiteboardSlot","    case thirdWhiteboardSlot","    \/* ... *\/","}"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This enum can then be passed into the corresponding "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/Whiteboard\/documentation\/Whiteboard"},{"type":"text","text":" methods.  However, while less error-prone than using a hard-coded index number, there is still the danger of posting a whiteboard message to the wrong slot.  Strongly typed whiteboard messages are safer and avoid this problem altogether. For details, see:"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/Whiteboard\/documentation\/Whiteboard\/TypeSafety"}]}]}]}]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":2,"patch":0},"sections":[],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/whiteboard\/messageslots"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/Whiteboard\/documentation\/Whiteboard\/MessageSlots","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The shared memory region that constitutes the whiteboard is subdivided into individual fixed and equal-size message slots.  For the whiteboard, this is simply a subdivision of memory that carries no semantic meaning.  The Swift "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/Whiteboard\/documentation\/Whiteboard"},{"type":"text","text":" inherits its sizes from the underlying "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/mipalgu\/gusimplewhiteboard"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation."}],"kind":"article","metadata":{"roleHeading":"Article","title":"Whiteboard Message Slots","role":"article","modules":[{"name":"Whiteboard"}]},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/Whiteboard\/documentation\/Whiteboard"]]},"references":{"doc://Whiteboard/documentation/Whiteboard/Whiteboard/slotCount":{"role":"symbol","title":"slotCount","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"static"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"slotCount"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Int","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Total number of message slots available on the whiteboard."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/Whiteboard\/documentation\/Whiteboard\/Whiteboard\/slotCount","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/whiteboard\/whiteboard\/slotcount"},"doc://Whiteboard/documentation/Whiteboard/TypeSafety":{"role":"article","title":"Type Safety","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Swift is a strongly-typed language that allows to use safe, strongly typed messages on the whiteboard."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/Whiteboard\/documentation\/Whiteboard\/TypeSafety","kind":"article","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/whiteboard\/typesafety"},"doc://Whiteboard/documentation/Whiteboard":{"role":"collection","title":"Whiteboard","abstract":[],"identifier":"doc:\/\/Whiteboard\/documentation\/Whiteboard","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/whiteboard"}}}